Package: EflowStats
Type: Package
Title: Returns Hydrologic Indicator stats for a given set of data
Version: 0.1
Date: 2017-04-04
Authors@R: c( person("Joe", "Mills", role = c("aut","cre"),
    email = "tmills@usgs.gov"))
